Executive Profile
Jim C. Walton  Chairman of the Board, Arvest Bank Group, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 1 Board Members in 1 different organizations across 2 different industries.69--
Background

		Mr. Jim C. Walton serves as the Chairman of the Board and Chief Executive Officer of Arvest Bank Group Inc., a group of banks operating in 91 communities in the states of Arkansas, Oklahoma and Missouri. Mr. Walton joined Wal-Mart and worked for four years in its real estate area. He left Wal-Mart in 1975 and joined the Walton's diversified family business, Walton Enterprises. He served as Chairman and Member of the Board at Community Publishers, Inc. He serves as a ... Director of Arvest Bank Group Inc. Mr. Walton served as a Director of Wal-mart Stores Inc., since September 28, 2005 until June 3, 2016. Mr. Walton attended the University of Arkansas in Fayetteville and Graduated with a Marketing Degree in 1971.Read Full Background




